    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through Anxiety and Creativity, follow the story of Noa. Chroma is a third-person 3D solo adventure game in which you play as Noa, an art student who evolves within her creativity. You will evolve through fantastic and dreamlike environments devoid of colors. With the help of her companion, bring back colors and life to the world in order to progress and understand what Noa is going through. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RECOLORATION:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To progress in this universe, you will be accompanied by Chroma, your blue slime companion. Thanks to him, you will be able to recolor and bring life back to the environment around you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317740/extras/3b8da88686090528e2d1a6c56c41557d.poster.avif?t=1732810384\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317740/extras/3b8da88686090528e2d1a6c56c41557d.webm?t=1732810384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317740/extras/3b8da88686090528e2d1a6c56c41557d.mp4?t=1732810384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLATFORMING: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move agilely and precisely through the environment to reach your goal. Revitalize your surroundings to help them grow and progress.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317740/extras/66bff51a6c13a66c33f221687b49332c.poster.avif?t=1732810384\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317740/extras/66bff51a6c13a66c33f221687b49332c.webm?t=1732810384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317740/extras/66bff51a6c13a66c33f221687b49332c.mp4?t=1732810384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NARRATION: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journey, the story will be narrated by Noa herself through fragments of memories, phrases scattered throughout the environment, and the scenery around you. You will also have access to Noa's journal, which will be filled as your adventure progresses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317740/extras/07c74a6588e45045a2ed1313dc810d0b.poster.avif?t=1732810384\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317740/extras/07c74a6588e45045a2ed1313dc810d0b.webm?t=1732810384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317740/extras/07c74a6588e45045a2ed1313dc810d0b.mp4?t=1732810384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
